{"layoutParsingResults": [{"prunedResult": {"page_count": null, "width": 1932, "height": 2679, "model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_seal_recognition": true, "use_table_recognition": true, "use_formula_recognition": true, "use_chart_recognition": false, "use_region_detection": true, "format_block_content": false, "markdown_ignore_labels": ["number", "footnote", "header", "header_image", "footer", "footer_image", "aside_text"]}, "parsing_res_list": [{"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "午、仁午、成乐、铁成", "block_bbox": [290, 240, 698, 287], "block_id": 0, "block_order": 1}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "曾孙：忠信、法信、恒信、荣信、五生、杜信、捌成、小九、玉信、学信、好信、韶信、鹤庆、志信、石屯、金钟、敬立\n", "block_bbox": [285, 299, 1743, 410], "block_id": 1, "block_order": 2}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "二零零三年清明立", "block_bbox": [371, 422, 707, 465], "block_id": 2, "block_order": 3}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "注：此碑入谱时改正了错字，而称谓之不明未改。洪洞迁渑原因亦误：实有朝廷诏令，由富裕之窄乡移贫穷之宽乡。\n", "block_bbox": [286, 481, 1743, 588], "block_id": 3, "block_order": 4}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "渑池", "block_bbox": [107, 715, 183, 890], "block_id": 4, "block_order": 5}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "杜氏宗谱", "block_bbox": [110, 1008, 181, 1395], "block_id": 5, "block_order": 6}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "重建南张村杜氏祖坟碑记", "block_bbox": [369, 664, 828, 706], "block_id": 6, "block_order": 7}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "吾杜氏祖坟始建于清乾隆年间，位于今义马市银杏路西段水厂对面路南，距路约五十米。祖坟葬吾姓十世祖若甫十一世祖含章等以下五代。若甫公关心族谊，创修渑池杜氏宗谱；含章公为乾隆六十年举人，撰始祖碑，其人其事均载入渑池县志。宗祠内存懿德碑。因其地建设美景瑞园小区，祖坟遂于公元二九年元月十八日迁移。为弘扬祖德、启迪后人，经吾族十七世至十九世共议，在渑池县天池镇龙潭沟之西坡卜建新茔，以安祖灵，其地呈椅形，虎踞龙盘，诚为宝地。为使后世铭记，特撰碑文，刻之贞石，以传千古。", "block_bbox": [281, 722, 1747, 1128], "block_id": 7, "block_order": 8}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "义马市千秋镇郭庄张村杜氏阖族仝立公元二零零九年四月吉日\n", "block_bbox": [371, 1141, 1031, 1243], "block_id": 8, "block_order": 9}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "七、《渑池县志》（民国17年）中有关杜姓的记载", "block_bbox": [461, 1321, 1556, 1373], "block_id": 9, "block_order": 10}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "卷二古迹·陵墓", "block_bbox": [286, 1440, 562, 1484], "block_id": 10, "block_order": 11}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "举人杜含章墓：在治东北孟岭村北原。", "block_bbox": [284, 1500, 968, 1547], "block_id": 11, "block_order": 12}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "卷五民政一·赈恤", "block_bbox": [287, 1561, 646, 1605], "block_id": 12, "block_order": 13}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "赈灾碑：光绪丁丑大饥，户部主事赵成杰、成俊兄弟立赈灾社，首捐粟豆二百石以为倡：闫表青捐三十石，……杜明德……·二石，……。设立粥厂，并按户分给极贫，一方赖之。碑，一存仁村关帝庙，一存槐圪塔村。", "block_bbox": [284, 1620, 1742, 1790], "block_id": 13, "block_order": 14}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "三九一", "block_bbox": [117, 2029, 168, 2133], "block_id": 14, "block_order": 15}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "卷四科第", "block_bbox": [289, 1801, 503, 1847], "block_id": 15, "block_order": 16}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "举人：杜宣，永乐癸卯，光禄寺丞。\n清副贡优贡：杜嘉林，咸丰己未，武涉训导。\n清举人：杜含章乾隆乙卯，详“儒林“。\n清岁贡：杜曰贤。\n\n清例贡捐纳：杜廷行，布经历衔。\n清掾吏：杜廷选从九品，分发湖北。\n民国县议会议员：杜佐唐。\n\n时政\n\n学界：杜佐唐，乙种农校长。\n\n公界：杜峰蝶，农村组织委员会委员。\n", "block_bbox": [285, 1861, 1134, 2459], "block_id": 16, "block_order": 17}], "layout_det_res": {"boxes": [{"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9503141045570374, "coordinate": [281.72540283203125, 722.614501953125, 1747.446533203125, 1128.85595703125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.88714200258255, "coordinate": [285.03363037109375, 299.4461975097656, 1743.179931640625, 410.0247497558594]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.885923445224762, "coordinate": [286.61358642578125, 481.82391357421875, 1743.09228515625, 588.0839233398438]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8776501417160034, "coordinate": [284.32720947265625, 1620.16064453125, 1742.070068359375, 1790.93408203125]}, {"cls_id": 0, "label": "paragraph_title", "score": 0.8456780910491943, "coordinat